headline: ResMed (RMD) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: ResMed (RMD) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +4.59% and +2.30%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
